Performance analyzer and report generator
  Supports easy way of gathering work information             +
  Supports timing of subintervals and loops                   +
  Supports OpenCL timing                                      -
  Generates reports in XML formats                            +
  Converts XML reports to html documents                      +
  Contains GUI to view reports                                -
  Converts XML reports to text format for automatic analysis  +

Command Line and Configuration
  Supports key, flag and action argument types                            +
  Automatically adds --help action                                        +
  Supports integer, float and string argument types                       +
  Supports argument arrays                                                +
  Supports configuration files in .ini and .xml formats                   -
  Supports correctness check for general cases (range of variable,        +
                                                correctness of filename)  +